who are equally handy at a bench or a bayonet.

28
00:05:42,579 --> 00:05:55,286
Trenches, antitank ditches and new railway tracks are another aspect of the endless burden which the Soviet people gladly shoulder for victory.

29
00:05:55,307 --> 00:05:58,548
Chula was a junction in the Red Army drive to the west, not a terminus.

30
00:05:58,708 --> 00:06:05,052
