Outside Moscow, those same jackboots are shuffling and stamping to conjure a little warmth back into frostbitten feet.

46
00:07:06,661 --> 00:07:11,223
These same bullies know today the misery of hunger and weariness and despair.

47
00:07:11,244 --> 00:07:18,168
